cky was 15 when she won her first gold medal.\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2630, \"end\": 2643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her first gold medal\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Who can make sense of something like that at 15?\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2734, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sense\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2704}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2717}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Full appreciation is the gift that McIntosh unknowingly wrapped for herself Monday night, to be opened at a much later date.\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2771, \"end\": 2779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7471716597818746e-14, \"text\": \"McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Full appreciation\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2753}, {\"ngram\": \"the gift\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2765}, {\"ngram\": \"a much later date\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For now, she at least seems to have avoided the traps that can come with others\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 assumption of greatness.\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2968, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the traps\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"others\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 assumption\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2954}, {\"ngram\": \"greatness\", \"from\": 2958, \"to\": 2967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Somebody asked if she felt any r